column5: Golbys.   Can you amagin that. Well I can ,as that port does bring in the big transport frieghters from around the world. Can you amagine the kid that caught one and his dad crushed it with his foot and said,NO DINNER FOR YOU. For those that caught a perch or rock bass,they did snatch some great prizes.
And here I thought it was going to be an OOS musky with a OOS bass in its mouth.
"Can you amagine the kid that caught one and his dad crushed it with his foot"....in front of a crowd of kids and parents....
Where in midland were the kids fishing for the day?
From the tv news it looked like the docks right in down town Midland.
